All-new episodes
of Proven Innocent Fridays.

00:09.777 --> 00:11.545
And check out
our other hit shows...

00:11.579 --> 00:14.315
The Resident, 9-1-1, and Empire.

00:14.348 --> 00:15.916
Only on Fox.

00:17.017 --> 00:18.852
Previously on Proven Innocent...

00:18.886 --> 00:20.088
You make me a better person.

00:20.121 --> 00:21.755
I think that I might
even be able to be

00:21.789 --> 00:23.124
a good example for Nathan.

00:23.157 --> 00:25.993
You really think
that Rosemary joined a cult?

00:26.026 --> 00:27.461
- Who else is there?
- Sarah Tawney.

00:27.495 --> 00:29.663
We're trying to figure out
what the "R" stood for.

00:29.697 --> 00:31.965
I'm guessing
your cult leader, Ravi?

00:31.999 --> 00:33.577
If he can give you some
evidence that might help

00:33.601 --> 00:35.136
reopen Rosemary's murder case...

00:35.169 --> 00:37.471
you could find yourself
sitting second chair

00:37.505 --> 00:39.207
in the biggest trial
of the year.

00:39.240 --> 00:41.041
Madeline chased after Rosemary.

00:41.075 --> 00:42.810
She was carrying that lantern.

00:42.843 --> 00:45.313
Madeline Scott, you are
under arrest for the murder

00:45.346 --> 00:46.680
of Rosemary Lynch.

00:51.485 --> 00:52.986
Good morning.

00:53.020 --> 00:55.189
Yesterday my office
executed an arrest warrant

00:55.223 --> 00:57.658
for Madeline Scott
for the murder

00:57.691 --> 01:00.060
of 17-year-old Rosemary Lynch.

01:00.094 --> 01:03.231
Ten years ago, her conviction
was regrettably vacated,

01:03.264 --> 01:04.831
but this office...

01:04.864 --> 01:08.469
My office... has always been
convinced of her guilt.

01:11.038 --> 01:15.176
Right now, Madeline Scott
is in prison, awaiting bail.

01:15.209 --> 01:17.411
As a prosecutor,
it's my job to produce

01:17.445 --> 01:21.549
credible evidence of guilt
beyond any reasonable doubt.

01:21.582 --> 01:23.251
I promise you today,

01:23.284 --> 01:24.652
I will do that.

01:24.685 --> 01:26.496
- What the hell's going on in here?
- Contraband search.

01:26.520 --> 01:27.964
You can rip my room apart
all you want,

01:27.988 --> 01:29.299
but you can't take my personal
belongings, okay?

01:29.323 --> 01:33.093
I'm entitled
papers, pens and my case files.

01:33.127 --> 01:37.398
Because unlike our original
trial, we are now 100% sure

01:37.431 --> 01:40.401
we have the weapon
Madeline Scott used

01:40.434 --> 01:42.436
to murder Rosemary Lynch.

01:42.470 --> 01:44.181
- Please, look... you need to give those back.
- Hey.

01:44.205 --> 01:46.507
You're not going nowhere,
so bitch and moan

01:46.540 --> 01:48.876
to someone who cares.

01:48.909 --> 01:51.745
Justice will finally be served.

01:51.779 --> 01:56.284
The Lynch family
will finally have closure,

01:56.317 --> 01:59.320
because the monster
who murdered their loved one

01:59.353 --> 02:01.322
will spend the rest of her life

02:01.355 --> 02:03.191
behind bars.

